Package org.botblock.javabotblockapi

Enum Site

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Site>
      • org.botblock.javabotblockapi.Site
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Site>
    public enum Site
extends Enum<Site>
    Enum class containing all sites currently supported by BotBlock.org.

    Those names can be used in methods of either the BotBlockAPI, the GetAction or the PostAction class.

    Since:
    v2.1.0
